creator: NUMAXES
descriptionHtml:
The Canicom GPS application displays your position and the position of your dog(s) on a map or satellite view.

It offers many possibilities:

1) Displays dog position either on a map or satellite view,
2) Displays your position either on a map or satellite view,
3) Electronic compass directs you to retrieve your dog(s),
4) Training function for remote recall,
5) Allows you to create and save tags,
6) Geo-fence function allows you to get notified when a dog exits the area,
7) Lets you share dog position with other people,
8) Route planner calculates the best route to your dog(s).
descriptionShort: The Canicom GPS application is compatible with the NUM'AXES tracking system.
